title: Buffy the Vampire Slayer season 9  023 (2013) (Tablet Edition)
description:
This is from the original scanner. I adjusted the resolution and 

compressed the file for easier reading on tablets and ereaders. I 

have added 'Tablet Edition' to the name to avoid confusion.

Enjoy and please seed back.
  


Buffy the Vampire Slayer Season 9 23

By:   	Andrew Chambliss, Karl Story, Georges Jeanty, Michelle 

Madsen, Phil Noto	
Type:   	Comics
Genres:   	Action-Adventure, Horror
Series:   	Buffy the Vampire Slayer
Publisher:   	Dark Horse	
Pub. Date:  	July 10, 2013


Dawn's life hangs in the balance, and Buffy will stop at nothing to 

save her little sis. Willow, Xander, and Buffy reunite to save the 

girl they love and begin a journey that reveals betrayal amongst 

the ranks as they descend into the mysterious Deeper Well, former 

home of Illyria and many powerful Old Ones.


* Executive produced by Joss Whedon!


"Season 9's strongest quality so far is that it feels very much 

like a return to basics for the franchise. Essentially, Season 9 

tells stories in the style of the original TV show without having 

to make the same sorts of budgetary concessions." IGN
